title: Episode 106 - The Two Germany's 1950 - 60 | Part 2 - West Germany
itunes:author: The History of the Cold War Podcast
itunes:summary:
In this episode we examine West Germany in contrast to East Germany 1950-1960. We will discuss the West German economic miracle, Germany's membership in NATO and its integration with the rest of western Europe.

For pictures for this episode and more go to our website at:  www.historyofthecoldwarpodcast.com/
